{"tid":1221190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"知名電競手直播失言：我不在意香港發生的事 遭港台網民鬧爆後致歉","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T08:00:11.000Z","uid":48093,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"18f0745923e67a7ca90846c72426c6e060e93132","tid":1221190,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190614/large/1560492682_d90d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190614%2Flarge%2F1560492682_d90d.jpg&h=0be70bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全城關注《逃犯條例》修訂，各路網紅、KOL紛紛表態反惡法。但曾於熱門電子遊戲《英雄聯盟》世界賽奪冠的香港選手劉偉健（Toyz），昨日（13日）晚上在遊戲直播中直指自己「政治冷感」、「為甚麼這個法例能讓103萬人出來遊行？」，隨即引來港、台兩地網民炮轟。劉失言後關閉直播，直至深夜向網民道歉，但網民未有接受，並呼籲取消訂閱其直播及影片頻道，隨即他的頻道訂閱數字因事件後直線下跌。<br />\n<br />\n事源劉昨晚約9時於遊戲直播平台Twitch上進行直播，其間被網民追問對《逃犯條例》修訂的看法，之後用國語回覆「我一點都不在意香港發生的事情，可以嗎？我政治冷感」，更指「這件事情（修例）不管它最後通過還是沒通過，我覺得對我的生活完全不影響的，為甚麼這個法例能讓103萬人出來遊行？」。<br />\n網民隨即在直播平台聊天室炮轟，稱劉「可悲」、對他「失望」。劉之後見狀關閉直播，但有關直播片段已被轉載到港、台各大網上討論區，包括高登、連登及巴哈姆特等，兩地網民幾乎一面倒斥責劉，有網民更要求劉永久關閉直播頻道。"},{"pid":"78248eac6187aa4c4642537531382625701e6696","tid":1221190,"uid":148987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1fc1f0674521753327d1dc60b73bf1f87ce74ab3","tid":1221190,"uid":255624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586714c2bd75dafc542c6a8a823af01a1c6ae4ba","tid":1221190,"uid":197213,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"真係敢言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我信佢係講真話，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448b7ed0fbdeb09b40d27ea678a1ebc5c13af45a","tid":1221190,"uid":164684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我擔心條例未過佢已經有影響"},{"pid":"b43385def9c0b8e2321334b1818643e7b83b04e1","tid":1221190,"uid":164932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"果然係弱智仔"},{"pid":"462c69fdfd687a5ff924640466c646afc5788e27","tid":1221190,"uid":6030,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"淨係識打機既垃圾"},{"pid":"b640828708ddd9c9c59396686b16bde01c2e7f66","tid":1221190,"uid":155095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ZWMAff9eZPw/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FZWMAff9eZPw%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d67597ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"399e28b2ebd715c8c1795e903f123d2be2e70d9b","tid":1221190,"uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:48:45.000Z","msg":"don't make stupid people famous"},{"pid":"351fb6450dd0d747a1ea1a9bafd168cae0f824e0","tid":1221190,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:48:46.000Z","msg":"打機打到腦殘"},{"pid":"66a7628253e4784934c4d2a7e02a6387b4277be4","tid":1221190,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"香港警察 社會垃圾<br />\n人民奴隸 賣港惡賊<br />\n底層散仔毅進弱智仔<br />\n就算大學學歷都係垃圾科，無得揀先去做警犬嘅廢柴，蛇鼠一窩"},{"pid":"c57f5f7c2badb30726ef62a4dac852201043cf17","tid":1221190,"uid":140454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"連蘋果都報<br />\n佢真係仆硬街了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/